*Nedelju* dana je prošlo od tada. (A week has passed since then.)

Nedeljom* se završavaju obaveze. (The obligations are finished on Sundays.)

U nedelju* ću biti slobodan. (I will be free on Sunday.)

*Nedeljom* je prošla večnost. (An eternity has passed on Sunday.)

*Nedelju* dana je prošlo od kada je počelo. (A week has passed since it started.)